<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Huququlator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css">
</head>
<body class="main-page-body">
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <% if (loggedIn) { %>
            <!-- Logged-in view -->
            <span>Welcome, <%= username %></span>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <a href="/">Calculator</a>
                <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/upload">Upload Transactions</a>
                <a href="/filter-rules">Categorization rules</a>
                <a href="/transactions">View Transactions</a>
                <a href="/logout">Log out</a>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <!-- Logged-out view -->
            <div class="navbar-left">
                <a href="/">Calculator</a>
                <a href="/help">Help</a>
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <a href="/login">Login</a>
                <a href="/register">Register</a>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <h1>About Huququlator</h1>
        <p>Huququlator is a tool designed to simplify the process of calculating Ḥuqúqu’lláh for members of the Bahá’í faith. It helps users determine their net assessable wealth, track payments, and understand the intricacies of the law.</p>

        <div class="about-section">
            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <div class="about-item" id="about1">
                <h2 onclick="toggleAbout('about1')">Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="about-content expanded">
                    <p>Huququlator aims to support members of the Bahá’í community by providing an accessible and accurate platform for fulfilling the sacred obligation of Ḥuqúqu’lláh. Our mission is to empower users to manage their financial responsibilities with clarity and confidence.</p>
                </div>
                <button class="view-more" onclick="toggleAbout('about1')">Collapse</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/about.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
